extracted_text:
Shiflina Nilofar P
+91 9342003015 |  |  | Ayapakkam, Chennai | 
Results-driven and enthusiastic Data Engineering fresher with hands-on experience in Python, SQL, and data analysis. Eager to contribute to building efficient data pipelines and infrastructure as a Big Data Engineer. Seeking to grow within a dynamic tech environment and help organizations harness the power of big data for actionable insights.
Education
Bachelor Of Computer Applications (BCA)
Queen Mary’s College, Chennai | 08/2022 – 05/2025 | CGPA : 7.4
Higher Secondary
Girls Government Higher Secondary School, Ayapakkam | 06/2021 – 05/2022 | Percentage : 84%
Skills
Languages & Tools: Python (Intermediate), PL/SQL, MySQL, NumPy, Pandas, Excel, Tableau
Data Engineering Tools: ETL Concepts, Data Modeling, Data Cleaning
Soft Skills: Communication, Problem-Solving, Teamwork, Project Management

Projects
Inventory Management System
Built using Python, Pandas, and MySQL.
Automated inventory tracking, restocking alerts, and reporting.
Designed interactive dashboards for stock visualization.
Certifications
Python Programming – GUVI
SQL Gold Badge – HackerRank
Achievements
1st Runner-Up – Web Designing Competition (The New College, 2025)
1st Runner-Up – Coding Challenge (Python) (MCC College, 2025)
Winners – Project Expo with Team Project (Measi Institute of Information Technology, 2025)
Simulation
Accenture North America Data Analytics and Visualization Job Simulation on Forage - June 2024
Completed a simulation focused on advising a hypothetical social media client as a Data Analyst at Accenture
Cleaned, modelled and analyzed 7 datasets to uncover insights into content trends to inform strategic decisions
Prepared a PowerPoint deck and video presentation to communicate key insights for the client and internal stakeholders
